{"tid":1848972,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（有救了）疑似搵到土炮醫治武漢肺炎嘅方法！！","createTime":"2020-01-28T18:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T05:43:05.000Z","uid":207078,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d1c3c0900a9512ab3c990dec7e3358d4f599c6","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"係知道點醫之前首先要講下今次呢隻病嘅病理先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻菌入咗人體之後，人體會啟動免疫系統嚟清除呢啲外來入侵者，不過<span style=\"color: red;\"> 呢隻病毒會誘使免疫系統過度反應</span>，之後傷害到身體的組織，呢個係引發肺炎的主要機制，就好似今次新型冠狀病毒最常攻擊的是肺臟<br />\n<br />\n咁既然係令免疫系統有過度反應先會有事，即刻免疫系統正常反應甚至係唔作出任何反應就會無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋可以睇睇愛滋病，愛滋病毒係會攻擊免疫細胞，會將淋巴細胞KO，<span style=\"color: red;\">即係將身體的監控同埋警衛都無效化 </span>。咁講法即係將愛滋病毒打入中咗武漢肺炎嘅患者到，佢嘅免疫系統就會react唔到，然後就唔會有事！名符其實<span style=\"color: red;\">以毒攻毒！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9d924e26abfaadc37ae2f00fa437918ebb63ea","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:39:13.000Z","msg":"有救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f82a3bda4afd8dd00d276b2f3949c6f4e14952","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:41:08.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"24b114ad4dffbf5bd48ffc4a3ff64dde9b0fcd0d","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"有救啦"},{"pid":"210c481bdd45258a97f683a4cac353f2dec29c1f","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:43:42.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"3a1f30c357f3d9f0d147516f6f022aeaab88a0c9","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:43:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"faacafd03894663bc04bf24da5c20381aff8cc60","tid":1848972,"uid":207078,"like":0,"disl